{"tid":926221,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食譜][聖誕送禮]—熱朱古力 Super Rich Hot Chocolate","createTime":"2018-12-03T09:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T07:13:24.000Z","uid":182683,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1db20007074edf36f7e2a09de08095a0a97396","tid":926221,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"聖誕緊係要送野溝囡囡！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會連續出5個送禮食譜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條片放左係Igtv！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/Bq6yZN0Hv56/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=147mbevu6frep\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FBq6yZN0Hv56%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D147mbevu6frep&d=4YVk5A5T4iIYUIwemLe3IsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7a6fd17f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/Bq6yZN0Hv56/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=147mbevu6frep</a><br />\n<br />\n依個食譜極簡單！攪混曬啲野就整完！！因為加左粟粉同用真朱古力，沖出黎同你係法國飲個啲又杰又濃嘅一模一樣！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加少少野做裝飾，個包裝整到靚靚地，包你一定有女過聖誕！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZiKj3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZiKj3e.png&h=e72af2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n<br />\n黑朱古力200g (70%或以上)(買你覺得最好食個隻)<br />\n可可粉 100g (買靚少少嘅dutch cocoa powder) <br />\n幼糖霜 70g-100g(睇你鍾意飲幾甜)<br />\n美綠/好立克 50g <br />\n粟粉 40g-50g(睇你鍾意杰啲定稀啲)<br />\n鹽 少少 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n<br />\n綿花糖 (大同細)<br />\n朱古力<br />\nM&amp;m<br />\n木匙羹<br />\n彩針<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n做法:<br />\n1.攪碎朱古力<br />\n朱古力提早放雪櫃30分鐘先，用手/刀將大塊嘅朱古力變細塊，放入食物處理器開慢速切到變細粒狀，再開快速切到接近粉末狀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ivTXQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ivTXQH.png&h=4070cd7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKSZTo4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKSZTo4.png&h=32990fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.熱朱古力<br />\n將其餘粉狀材料攪埋一齊就搞掂，如果覺得啲粉唔夠幼細可以倒番入部機到攪多10幾秒，但記住唔好攪咁耐，啲朱古力會溶。<br />\n最後拎個樽入住放室溫就可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9phE4r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9phE4r.png&h=88a811b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qj5D8XR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqj5D8XR.png&h=2459aced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.沖朱古力<br />\n我通常就用飲個隻杯倒啲奶入去量左先，再倒入個煲到煮到滾，跟住熄火落朱古力粉攪到溶曬就飲得，飲個時落幾粒綿花糖。<br />\n落幾多粉自己個人喜好，沖一次第二次就會預岩落幾多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nt3ipwV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnt3ipwV.png&h=acc4edf1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkRDpwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkRDpwW.png&h=72f8cf40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.裝飾<br />\n-綿花糖<br />\n溶左啲朱古力落吱袋，吱自己想要嘅樣，唔駛好靚有心就得！最後痴粒m&amp;m上個鼻到，等乾。<br />\n入樽個時放啲細粒綿花糖係底，小心啲放有樣個啲貼住個樽面比人睇到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QwNOMLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQwNOMLz.png&h=a730946d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGcCE5B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGcCE5B.png&h=9d9b9e39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJBshSh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJBshSh.png&h=3e5fe7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72cvfGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72cvfGk.png&h=23cd8a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-木匙羹<br />\n溶左啲朱古力，浸半支匙羹入去，放平係牛油紙再撒啲彩針/m&amp;m上去，放室溫等乾。<br />\n其實撒咩都冇所謂，可以打碎啲餅/果仁撒上去都得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpFD80s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpFD80s.png&h=d37035d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fyqO0C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fyqO0C.png&h=315fb78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTNfrNM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTNfrNM.png&h=6c53a953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包裝個啲我都唔係好識，我都係上網睇人點整，個朱古力就一定正嫁啦！加埋綿花糖等於玩曬！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲野整得唔靚唔緊要，最緊要有心整，囡囡收到一定感動到即刻喊，攬住你想同你過聖誕！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=4YVk5A5T4iIYUIwemLe3IsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=dc099ed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c9e6130468d0bf90ad6d5d5e91b2cc2e3b39cd","tid":926221,"uid":55941,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲完即刻糖尿都似"},{"pid":"3cb180aba00adfcb1ca7e32d5594a6e63cc308d4","tid":926221,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dad1b0c5ef8d5b731dc22ca7f5c6eef140d7af","tid":926221,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52c9e6130468d0bf90ad6d5d5e91b2cc2e3b39cd","tid":926221,"uid":55941,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲完即刻糖尿都似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔甜嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n除非你用牛奶朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b7f832ccdf962a048daff786be174ed6ddd2e5","tid":926221,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接用奶整溶佢要打粉先? 無用具喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebb25fb35481584c0c5398778bf3770e64b716b","tid":926221,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"如果自己飲係咪可以唔洗prep dark chocolate<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2ee8e5985a66831c73914f7ac3b09e39a95c89","tid":926221,"uid":142247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9b7f832ccdf962a048daff786be174ed6ddd2e5","tid":926221,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接用奶整溶佢要打粉先? 無用具喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:07:07.000Z","msg":"放落密實袋封實<br />\n用手meet到細細塊先佢先<br />\n之後鋪平個密實袋<br />\n搵個酒樽或者豉油樽係咁碌佢<br />\n覺得唔夠細再搵刀chop下佢<br />\n<br />\n窮撚整法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2e52e79474c5847a8e6561fffb1cb207965808","tid":926221,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ebb25fb35481584c0c5398778bf3770e64b716b","tid":926221,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"如果自己飲係咪可以唔洗prep dark chocolate<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:07:36.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/asset